Places to Visit in Jaipur

You just can't have enough of the places to visit in Jaipur as the Pink City, as Jaipur is called, is crammed full of historical Jaipur tourist places. In fact, in terms of sightseeing, the few other destinations in the country can match the beauty of historical sightseeing in Jaipur. Amongst the various wonderful attractions here, just some of the absolutely not to be missed places for sightseeing in Jaipur are Amber Fort, City Palace, Abhaneri Step Well, Galtaji Temple, and Jaigarh Fort.
